Self-Evaluation (Second Major Work in 2025)

This was my second major research and system development work in the year 2025. The project focused on building a safe and reliable LLM-based medical system using a multi-agent architecture.

Research Work and Industry Conference

This work was submitted and accepted in the Industry Track of an AI-ML Systems conference, highlighting its practical and industry relevance. I travelled to the conference and presented the work, explaining the system design, safety mechanisms, and results to an international audience. This helped showcase our work and organization in a real-world, industry-focused research forum.

