The differential diagnosis component of the system was developed by my colleague as part of our collaborative effort. My work mainly focused on system design, safety, integration, and evaluation.

Impact and Results

The system showed improved diagnostic accuracy and significantly better detection of unsafe prescriptions compared to baseline approaches. It demonstrates how LLMs can be safely used in healthcare by enforcing structured workflows and safety checks at the system level.

